{"tid":2497033,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"19歲人已經身家過億 人生勝利組","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T09:35:23.000Z","uid":390762,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cbfa8191e417d8dbb02af98d487234ef9cc7c632","tid":2497033,"uid":390762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:39:44.000Z","msg":"電話騙案在港發生多年，其中一宗去年發生的案件，受害人為90歲婆婆，被騙走共約2.5億港元款項，成為歷年涉及最高金額的假冒內地官員電話騙案。警方今(20日)表示，中區警區重案組第2隊經深入調查後，於3月25日在<span class=\"red\">天水圍區拘捕一名19歲姓黃男子</span>，涉嫌以欺騙手段取得財產。他現已獲准保釋候查，須於本月下旬向警方報到。案件仍在調查中，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n據了解，被捕青年就讀<span class=\"red\">香港理工大學1年級，</span><br />\n<br />\n人生已勝利，最高刑罰都係14年，你坐完14年出嚟，就已經身家過億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。香港人做成世都無一千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都係19歲，仲同樣住埋天水圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，點解你咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4ede50cc26cec16d8ac65997ae7dcf302d304f","tid":2497033,"uid":270943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:41:00.000Z","msg":"買bitcoin 出到黎唔洗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfcc83270f9b3cd7aead845c05f10a7221e723d","tid":2497033,"uid":219128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:42:30.000Z","msg":"佢好似係抽佣，得900百萬左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de0ab30f3a2cd450dc432359d0bce360b8bf7799","tid":2497033,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"公屋asso仔終於脫貧"},{"pid":"58d2786d25ec1abdf96282572f933949aceb40bf","tid":2497033,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:43:14.000Z","msg":"唔係好清楚，呃完人俾人查到唔係要嘔返出黎架咩"},{"pid":"922aa72d108a952b949a242bce85b6b97b315ec1","tid":2497033,"uid":390762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de0ab30f3a2cd450dc432359d0bce360b8bf7799","